Text:
Gutter Rainbows is the fifth solo album from American hip hop artist Talib Kweli. 
The album will be the first to be released by his imprint Talibra. The album will 
also be released digital only. On November 16th, It was announced that Duck Down 
Records will step in to see the album gets a CD release...
